text: Hana, how does it feel to wear the costume?

Um...
It was really hard to put on!

Oh... I see.
Is there anything else? Maybe in terms of how you feel?

Yeah, well...
I remembered something Producer said the other day.
He said, "The first unit costume will be the last."

So, for me, wearing the first unit costume
first means this is the last one.

I want Producer to cherish
the current me, hehe.
